{"title":"迎金日成元帅","authors":["田汉"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎金日成元帅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年第一届赴朝慰问，曾与廖承志同志等夜访金日成首相于平壤一小村。顷闻将军来访问北京，喜成三律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中朝不可分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤村寒夜谒将军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧天战火红如血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歼敌豪情盛似云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭绿悠悠流友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金刚屹屹纪殊勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾又报伸魔爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾杜冥顽只自焚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血凝成友谊花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年相处已如家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰封千里抬伤病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮火连天送饭茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女宵来填绣枕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怜翁今日整乌纱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骊歌纵唱何能别？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万泪如潮湿战车。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月来曾作厦门行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪涌波翻万炮鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许西风吹亚陆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定教星帜舞台澎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"移山倒海党人志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披发缨冠战友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他日将军如号唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘大陆一民兵。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}